Package: dryR
Type: Package
Title: Differential RhythmicitY analysis 
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Cedric Gobet and Benjamin Weger
Maintainer: The package maintainer <cedric.gobet@epfl.ch>
Description: DryR ( Differential RhythmicitY analysis in R) is a statistical
     framework based on model selection that is designed to detect and estimate changes 
     in rhythmic parameters (amplitude and phase) and mean expression in multiple conditions.
biocViews: Software, BiologicalQuestion
